            ::= { unisAclActiveEntry 2 }

        unisAclActiveVlanID OBJECT-TYPE
            SYNTAX Integer32
            MAX-ACCESS not-accessible
            STATUS current
            DESCRIPTION
                "The lower 16 bits is Vlan ID, the higher 16 bits,
                 if not zero, it describes the slot ID of the L3plus board.
