            MAX-ACCESS read-only
            STATUS current
            DESCRIPTION
                "The count of matched by the rule."
            ::= { unisAclNamedUserEntry 11 }

        unisAclNamedUserCountClear OBJECT-TYPE
            SYNTAX CounterClear
            MAX-ACCESS read-write
            STATUS current
            DESCRIPTION
